Bond Investor Directory

GLC Asset Management Group Ltd









GLC Asset Management Group Ltd



Overbond #336
Asset Management




                  Incorporated in: Canada
                


                  Asset Under Management ($B): 47.0
                



GLC Asset Management Group Ltd. is a privately owned asset management holding company. It primarily provides its services to corporations, pension plans, endowments, families, and business owners. Through its subsidiaries, the firm provides portfolio management and fund management services to its clients. GLC Asset Management Group Ltd. is based in Toronto, Canada with additional offices in London, Canada and Winnipeg, Canada. The firm operates as a subsidiary of The Great-West Life Assurance Company.

